  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>*Supervise and coordinate the daily operations of the food production teams, ensuring adherence to production schedules, quality standards, and safety protocols.</p><p>*Lead and mentor production staffs, including machine operators, line workers, and quality control personnel.</p><p>*Provide guidance, training, and support to maximize team performance.</p><p>*Enforce safety protocols and regulations to maintain a safe working environment for all production team members. Conduct regular safety inspections and address any safety concerns promptly.</p><p>*Maintain accurate production records, including batch records, production reports, and quality control documentation.</p><p>*Ensure that all production areas are cleaned and sanitized according to food safety standards. Implement improvements to enhance production processes.</p><p>*Able to carry heavy goods, roughly 20KG - 40KG.</p><p>*Need working on Saturday, Sunday, Public holiday and overtime.</p><p>*Able to work rotate shift and overtime.</p><p>Working Location: SENOKO</p>",
